Star Command.</i>

1417
01:07:11.390 --> 01:07:13.820
Okey. Okey.

1418
01:07:15.290 --> 01:07:18.160
Terima kasih banyak. suara hati.

1419
01:07:18.160 --> 01:07:21.960
Harmony. sayang. tolong nenek
tutup kedai malam ni.

1420
01:07:21.960 --> 01:07:24.900
Okey. Lepas tu kita
