1551
01:13:15.950 --> 01:13:17.620
Oh. inilah dia!

1552
01:13:17.620 --> 01:13:18.990
Kita akan pulang. Forky!

1553
01:13:19.990 --> 01:13:20.990
Huh?

1554
01:13:21.990 --> 01:13:23.560
Forky! Oh!

1555
01:13:24.560 --> 01:13:27.330
Tak. tak. tak. Woody. lihat!
Ia memang sedang terjadi!

1556
01:13:33.330 --> 01:13:36.440
<i>Saya Gabby Gabby.</i>
dan saya sayang kamu.

1557
01:13:37.440 --> 01:13:39.380
Aku rasa nak nangis.

1558
